ActBusiness Development Bank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of the Industry of MICHAEL CALYNIUK of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Stan Bracken-Horrocks.
